

========================================================
Liveinstaller is the installer for dsslive derivatives.


There are six major components to implement:

    *A user interface
    *A partitioning tool
    *A component to copy the filesystem into place
    *Language pack installation [todo]
    *Base system configuration
    *Boot loader installation

It needs:

    *An USS design
    *Gparted (patched)
    *Python
    *Peez2

Based on Guadalinex2005 installer
